OL,3,CUK inflation rises to 3.3% after Iran
OL,4,Cwar pushes up fuel prices
OL,6,FHigher fuel prices have led to
OL,7,Finflation rising to 3.3%, underlining
OL,8,Fthe impact of conflict in the Middle
OL,9,FEast on the cost of living, the Office
OL,10,Ffor National Statistics (ONS) has said.
OL,12,FThe ONS said on Wednesday the Consumer
OL,13,FPrice Index had risen to 3.3% in
OL,14,FMarch, up from 3% in February.
OL,16,FThese are the first inflation figures
OL,17,Fto be released since the US and Israel
OL,18,Fattacked Iran on February 28.
OL,20,FThe rise has pushed inflation to its
OL,21,Fhighest level since December.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/2
